body_html:
You can install provided wheel for python 3.5.
First, you download locally whl for python 3.4.
After that, you rename tensorflow-0.8.0-cp34-cp34m-linux_x86_64.whl to smth like tensorflow-0.8.0-cp35-none-linux_x86_64.whl

I hope this helps!
